results.title: Beautifully hand crafted 3 dimensional Intarsia Wood Art BEAR Picture Photo Frame
results.description:
Beautifully hand-crafted 3-dimensional Intarsia BEAR Wood Picture Photo Frame.

This piece of intarsia wood art required a lot of workmanship since it was hand-carved from 35 different pieces of wood with different thickness and glued together on a wood base to form this Bear Picture Frame.

Shelf display or wall hanging (the frame has a stand and also a hook on the back). 

All hand-carved using different kinds of wood to bring different colors for the piece. So, the colors of wood here are natural colors of wood. For this feature, it's almost like one-of-a-kind because next time if we make the same design again, it won't look exactly the same as the wood grain will change slightly. Also, each piece is hand-carved individually, so it's all unique. (The actual item you'll receive maybe very slightly different than what pictured since each piece is hand-crafted individually. However, we're confident you'll love the piece you receive regarding beauty and quality. We can confirm this because we have a lot of repeated happy customers).

Semi-gloss finish.

It would add a very beautiful & interesting item to your collection or make a perfect gift idea.....

Overall measurements : approximately 10.75" long X 7.75" high X 1" thick.

The frame measures approximately 7-3/8" high X 5.5" wide.

Photo area measures approximately 6" high X 4" wide.

results.title: Live Laugh Love Wood Sign, Custom Wood Sign, Country Primitive Wall Decor, Choice of color and size
results.description:
Live Laugh Love Wood Sign - 

Remind yourself or loved ones of what's important - to live in the moment, be sure to laugh, and above all to always love!

Custom painted in your choice of size and color.  Small size shown is perfect for a tiered tray or a wreath ornament, larger is great for your wall!

SIZE:
Your choice of:
--Approx 5.25 x 6.5 inches (shown on white sign)
--Approx 4 x 5 inches (shown on black sign)
--Measurements not exact, as we use pieces of reclaimed wood, not from a lumber yard.  Shape may be slightly irregular.

COLOR:
--Sign as shown has a white background, distressed and antiqued, with black lettering.
--You may choose a different color!  See additional photos for a few options.  Let us know what you'd like in the personalization section.
--Lettering is freehand painted in off-white, white, or black
--Wood look/grain will vary from photo, as the wood is very unique from piece to piece.

OUR PROCESS:
We create our signs start to finish, each one painted freehand without patterns or stencils, ensuring a unique piece of decor that can't be found in any department store!  When you purchase one of our signs, you're buying a little piece of art right out of our studio!

OUR WOOD:
All our signs are painted in reclaimed wood found throughout Washington state - torn down homes and barns, old fences, cast-offs from builders, etc.  Each piece of wood is unique, with variations in grain, cracks, knots, slight bowing, and individual character - perfectly imperfect!  This particular sign is made from Western red cedar.

FINISHING:
--Sides and back are painted to match
--Sealed on all sides with indoor satin varnish, sign on the back by artist
--Ready to hang, with sawtooth or jute twine hanger.

CARE:
--Keep out of direct sunlight
--Sealed for indoor use.  If kept out of direct exposure to sun and the elements, sign will be OK outdoors in a covered area, though it will weather over time.
--If you want to hang outside in the elements, seal with an outdoor sealant

***MADE TO ORDER*** - Will be made in the same manner as the sign in photo, but will not be exactly as it appears in the picture.  Hand lettering and natural wood make each sign look a little different!
